Thorntons Says Chairman Spreckelsen to Retire Within 12 Months

-- B y   D a r a   D o y l e
-- 
2011-09-27T06:08:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/thorntons-says-chairman-spreckelsen-to-retire-within-12-months.html
Thorntons Plc (THT)  said Chairman John
von Spreckelsen will retire within 12 months. “Accordingly, the
search for a suitable successor is being initiated,” the
company said.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
